<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    table, td, th {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 80%;
    }
    td {
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .table_padding td {
      padding: 12px;
    }
    tr:nth-child(even){background-color: #f2f2f2}
  </style>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />

</head>
<body>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 35px">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1><span style="color: #1abc9c; ">Dobro došli </span><%= @email %>! <small> Argentum Vita d.o.o.</small></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4 col-md-ofset-4">
        <%= image_tag "av.png", width:"200px;",style: "padding-top: 18px;" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h3>Uspješno ste se registrirali na stranicu!</h3>
    <h4>Kako bi potvrdili svoj račun kliknite na link: <span><%= link_to 'Potvrdi moj račun', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></span></h4>
  </div>
  <hr>

  <h4 style="margin-top:25px; margin-bottom:25px;">Mail za kontakt i upite:<span> <%= mail_to "info@argentumvita.hr" %></span></h4>
  <hr>
  <h4  style="margin-top: 10px"><span style="color: #1abc9c; ">Argentum Vita d.o.o.</span></h4>
  <br/>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <small>Ako ste ovu poruku primili greškom ili vam nije namijenjena, ne koristite ju, ne kopirajte, ne distribuirajte, ne otvarajte privitke, odmah ju obrišite sa svog računalnog sustava i obavijestite pošiljatelja da ste to napravili. Hvala!</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>